casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-2468. Upper Arlington City Schools v. Franklin Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 91-G-673. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellant’s application .to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective March 30, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
